snippet.textDisplay: I have two teen aged sons and really regret for one of them not being a girl after listening to this soul stirring voice of Tanishka Sanghvi & Rekha Bharadwaj. A voice loaded with emotions, you did bring tears to roll down my cheeks endlessly. Wish to congratulate Sachin for this monumental arrangement, Coke Studio & MTV for quality sound as always.I consider this as the best thing ever happened to "Unplugged" music in the world. Great effort, great melody. Literally forgot my worries. The scale change in the interlude with the Shehnai........truly Divinity dotted all over this track. Congratulations all the instrument players... backing vocals, brilliant....Keep it up.

snippet.textDisplay: Beautiful rendition, especially by this cute little girl Tanishka !! She's so cute and her voice is extremely soothing and soulful! Lending a beautiful touch of Gujarati Folk is Kirtidan Gadhvi, who delivers a sublime vocal performance that transcends the mood of the track! He has really brought Gujarati Folk Music traditions back into mainstream music !! Plus the lyrics are so deep, meaningful and heart-touching, both the Hindi and Gujarati parts! India needs more such independent music to flourish and enter the mainstream music industry! Coke Studio at MTV has definitely done a commendable job bringing all these super-talented artists and musicians together on a single platform! Hats off and continue promoting independent music! Looking forward to more and more compositions like this which will enchant us, enthrall us and soothe us! Period !
